review_blob: It is one of my favourite beers. Yesterday i visited brewery in Chios and met with kind owner Iakovios. Thanks to him for his great hospitality. The beer he served direct from was an unforgattable taste.
beer_name: Fresh Chios Beer / Frskia Mpra Chou (House Ale)

review_blob: Micro-breweries are improving in Turkey. And Gara Guzu is one of the pioneers. "Gara Guzu" means black sheep at the local dialect of Mugla city which is located in aegean region of Turkey. The brewery has only amber and blonde ale kinds at the moment but we are eagerly waiting new kinds. Gara Guzu Blonde Ale has a great aroma. I really like it.
